# Social Media Engagement Analytics on Instagram

This project explores engagement metrics (likes and comments) from Instagram to uncover actionable insights for social media influencers. Using advanced data analytics, the project identifies strategies to maximize user engagement and provides data-driven recommendations tailored for micro and macro influencers.

## Project Overview

Social media platforms like Instagram play a significant role in online marketing and audience engagement. This project focuses on analyzing a real-world Instagram dataset to address key questions related to post timing, content type, audience size, and engagement strategies.

### Goals
1. Identify the best times and days to post for maximum engagement.
2. Evaluate the impact of post characteristics like hashtags, sentiment, and text complexity on likes and comments.
3. Compare engagement strategies for micro-influencers (<50k followers) and macro-influencers (>=50k followers).
4. Provide actionable recommendations for influencers based on data insights.

